  <brief_title>Effects of Maternal Anti-HIV Treatment on Infants Born to HIV-Infected Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of Safety and Toxicity Among Infants Born to HIV-1-Infected Women Enrolled in Antiretroviral Treatment Protocols in Diverse Areas of the World</official_title>
  <sponsors>
